    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5758672/" class="title-link">被忽略的视角</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5758672"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/wqfengjun/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36282243-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wqfengjun/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">风君</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-01-28"
      class="main-meta">2013-01-28 20:55:24</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5758672_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  由于看过了《最寒冷的冬天》，所以当这本《最寒冷的冬天2》出来后，自然对其加以关注。不过仔细比较一下，发现本书虽名为“第二部”，实际和前书并无太大干系。《最寒冷的冬天》一书作者为美国记者哈伯斯塔姆，而本书作者是韩国前陆军上将白善烨。本书的韩文书名也和“最寒冷的...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5758672/#comments">(6回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">9有用 / 0没用</span>
